class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DArithmetic_progression=
&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D1" title=3D"Edit section: History"><span>e=
