edirect" title=3D"Zhang Qiujian">Zhang Qiujian</a>; in India to <a href=3D"=
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aryabhata" title=3D"Aryabhata">Aryabhata</a>,=
 <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brahmagupta" title=3D"Brahmagupta=
">Brahmagupta</a> and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bhaskara_II"=
