<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Sum">Sum</h2><span class=3D=
"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"=
https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DArithmetic_progression&amp;act=
ion=3Dedit&amp;section=3D2" title=3D"Edit section: Sum"><span>edit</span></=
a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
