"></span></dd></dl>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Derivation">Derivation</h3>=
<span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</sp=
an><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DArithmetic_progr=
ession&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D3" title=3D"Edit section: Derivation=
"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></spa=
n></div>
<figure class=3D"mw-default-size" typeof=3D"mw:File/Thumb"><a href=3D"https=
://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Animated_proof_for_the_formula_giving_the_sum=
_of_the_first_integers_1%2B2%2B...%2Bn.gif" class=3D"mw-file-description"><=
img src=3D"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Animat=
