}}=3D{\frac {a_{1}+a_{n}}{2}}.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/1700f9be7201eb91bcf92134675ac046176c02bc" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
