-align: -0.338ex; width:1.088ex; height:1.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle z}"=
></span> a positive complex number.
</p><p>Thus, if <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><s=
pan class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display:=
